0032#STR0032#ALL#MAN HOURS OF RISK EXPOSURE - Total of hours available to employer.
0033#STR0033#ALL#NUMBER OF ACCIDENTS WITHOUT LEAVE - One where the employee returns to their daily tasks in the same                  
0034#STR0034#ALL#day of the accident or the next day at the beginning of the work shift.     
0035#STR0035#ALL#NUMBER OF ACCIDENTS WITH LEAVE - One where the employee does not return to their daily tasks in the same           
0036#STR0036#ALL#day of the accident or the next day at the beginning of the work shift.     
0037#STR0037#ALL#TFSA - Number of accidents without leave x 1,000,000 / number of man hours of exposal.      
0038#STR0038#ALL#TFCA - Number of accidents with leave x 1,000,000 / number of man hours of exposal.         
